hopobject.body: What university do you go to? tylenol and ibuprofen not bringing fever down The increase in the fund is accompanied by compliments from the Global Fund’s Head of Africa and the Middle East, Lelio Marmora, who says Namibia is “progressing faster than anticipated” from malaria control to malaria pre-elimination. Namibia has also shown a notable decline malaria mortality. "Namibia is already ahead of targets established in the national strategic framework 2010 to 2016," Marmora said.
